TY  - JOUR
TI  - Capacity Pricing
AU  - Oren, Shmuel
AU  - Smith, Stephen
AU  - Wilson, Robert
AB  - [We study the problem of optimal pricing for a bundle of services characterized by two attributes (e.g., quantity and quality) and subject to capacity limitations or peakloading. An application is to services that take the form of a load-duration curve. Using separability assumptions on the demand and cost functions, we derive the optimal pricing policy for a monopolist seller. An example is solved completely.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1985
