TY  - JOUR
TI  - Existence of Cournot Equilibrium in Large Markets
AU  - Bamón, Rodrigo
AU  - Frayssé, Jean
AB  - [This paper examines the existence conditions of an oligopolistic equilibrium. We use the Cournot concept (the strategies are the production levels) in a partial equilibrium framework. We allow for U-shaped average cost curves and nonidentical firms. We show that an equilibrium exists if the demand is large. The main part of the proof is a new fixed point theorem for a class of noncontinuous mappings.]
C1  - Full publication date: May, 1985
