TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Computation of General Equilibrium in Economies with a Block Diagonal Pattern
AU  - van der Laan, Gerard
AB  - [In this paper we consider the computation of an equilibrium in a pure exchange economy with a block diagonal pattern. Such a structure appears in, e.g., international trade models. Utilizing the block diagonal pattern, the full equilibrium problem is reformulated as a problem on the product space of several lower-dimensional price-simplices. Some numerical results show the usefulness of this method.]
